Context: The George Brown College provides online examination delivery through Brightspace and offers two levels of optional virtual proctoring using Respondus Technology. Faculty members are required to run a test before implementing virtual proctoring services. Contact eLTI for assistance. Important information may change without notice, and students are responsible for verifying college fee requirements. The contact details for the college are: 416-415-2000, TTY: 1-877-515-5559, ask.george@georgebrown.ca, and their social media hub is also accessible.
